Package: libatomspace
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         libcogutil (>= 1.0.0),
         guile-3.0
Description: OpenCog AtomSpace hypergraph database (runtime)
 The AtomSpace is a weighted, labeled hypergraph database designed for
 knowledge representation and reasoning in artificial intelligence systems.
 .
 This package contains the shared libraries for runtime use.

Package: libatomspace-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libatomspace (= ${binary:Version}),
         libcogutil-dev (>= 1.0.0),
         guile-3.0-dev,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenCog AtomSpace hypergraph database (development files)
 The AtomSpace is a weighted, labeled hypergraph database designed for
 knowledge representation and reasoning in artificial intelligence systems.
 .
 This package contains the header files and development libraries.
